WARNING: this is work in progress. Don't try to use this unless you know what you're doing.

=============================
            Linux
=============================

Start by executing:
autoreconf -vif

To install add-ons into /path/to/XBMC:
./configure --prefix=/path/to/XBMC
make install

To build all PVR add-ons as .zip archives:
./configure
make zip

